OL,3,CPatients dying in hospital corridors
OL,4,Camid NHS 'national emergency', nurses
OL,5,Cwarn
OL,7,FNurses have declared a "national
OL,8,Femergency" in the NHS, warning that
OL,9,Fpatients are dying in hospital
OL,10,Fcorridors.
OL,12,FThe Royal College of Nursing (RCN)
OL,13,Frevealed patients are being left
OL,14,Fwithout access to oxygen and enduring
OL,15,Fintimate examinations in inappropriate
OL,16,Fcrowded areas.
