OL,4,Camid NHS 'national emergency', nurses
OL,5,Cwarn
OL,7,FAt the start of the union's annual
OL,8,Fconference in Newport, South Wales,
OL,9,Facting general secretary Professor
OL,10,FNicola Ranger will use her keynote
OL,11,Fspeech to declare a national
OL,12,Femergency, releasing a new report on
OL,13,Fclinical care in inappropriate areas.
OL,15,FThe RCN is calling for mandatory
OL,16,Freporting of patients cared for in
OL,17,Fcorridors to show the extent of
OL,18,Fhospital overcrowding.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G2/15
