OL,3,CPatients dying in hospital corridors
OL,4,Camid NHS 'national emergency', nurses
OL,5,Cwarn
OL,7,FPatients are regularly treated on
OL,8,Fchairs in corridors for extended
OL,9,Fperiods of time, sometimes days, said
OL,10,Fthe RCN.
OL,12,FA survey of almost 11,000 frontline
OL,13,Fnursing staff across the UK showed how
OL,14,Fwidespread the practice has become,
OL,15,Fsaid the RCN.
OL,17,FWhen asked about their most recent
OL,18,Fshift, almost two in five respondents
OL,19,Freported delivering care in an
OL,20,Finappropriate area, such as a corridor.
