OL,7,FAlmost seven in 10 said the care they
OL,8,Fdelivered in public compromised
OL,9,Fpatient privacy and dignity.
OL,11,FProf Ranger will tell the 3,000
OL,12,Fconference delegates that the
OL,13,Fsituation is a "tragedy" for the
OL,14,Fnursing profession.
OL,16,F"Our once world-leading services are
OL,17,Ftreating patients in car parks and
OL,18,Fstore cupboards.
OL,26,@uD@POUuD@XO]xD@AOU
