OL,3,CPatients dying in hospital corridors
OL,4,Camid NHS 'national emergency', nurses
OL,5,Cwarn
OL,7,F"The elderly are languishing on chairs
OL,8,Ffor hours on end and patients are
OL,9,Fdying in corridors. The horror of this
OL,10,Fsituation cannot be understated. It is
OL,11,Fa national emergency for patient
OL,12,Fsafety and today we are raising the
OL,13,Falarm.
OL,15,F"This is about honesty and
OL,16,Faccountability. Care being delivered
OL,17,Fin front of a fire exit isn't care.
OL,18,FSigning 'Do not resuscitate' orders in
OL,19,Fa corridor isn't care.
OL,26,@oD@AOUwD@AOU
