OL,8,Fdementia being in a corridor for hours
OL,9,Fwithout oxygen.
OL,11,FThey said: "When I arrived, she was in
OL,12,Fa wheelchair on a corridor with her
OL,13,Fdaughter. She was extremely agitated,
OL,14,Fcrying and confused. This care
OL,15,Fenvironment for any patient, never
OL,16,Fmind with dementia, was completely
OL,17,Finappropriate."
