OL,7,FThe new report says corridor care is
OL,8,F"a symptom of a system in crisis",
OL,9,Fwith patient demand in all settings,
OL,10,Ffrom primary to community and social
OL,11,Fcare, outstripping workforce supply.
OL,13,FThe result is patients left unable to
OL,14,Faccess care near their homes and
OL,15,Finstead being forced to turn to
OL,16,Fhospitals.
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@aO]
