OL,7,FSaffron Cordery, deputy chief
OL,8,Fexecutive at NHS Providers, said:
OL,9,F"These findings reflect the severe
OL,10,Fpressures facing the NHS, including
OL,11,Fhigh demand, lack of bed capacity and
OL,12,Fdelayed hospital discharge.
OL,14,F"No trust leader wants to treat
OL,15,Fpatients in corridors, store cupboards
OL,16,For other non-clinical areas as it
OL,17,Fcompromises quality of care, patient
OL,18,Fprivacy and dignity.
OL,26,@qD@AOUvD@AOU
