OL,5,Cwarn
OL,7,F"The deeply concerning experiences
OL,8,Fshared by frontline nurses highlight
OL,9,Fthe urgent need for more strategic
OL,10,Finvestment and planning.
OL,12,F"It's vital the next government
OL,13,Fproperly address the root causes of
OL,14,Fhospital overcrowding.
OL,16,F"Improving social care and community
OL,17,Fservices is also key to ensure
OL,18,Fpatients can be discharged safely and
OL,19,Fpromptly, freeing up hospital beds for
OL,20,Fthose most in need."
