OL,7,FWes Streeting, shadow health
OL,8,Fsecretary, said: "NHS nurses are
OL,9,Fsounding the alarm on the appalling
OL,10,Fstate of the NHS after 14 years of
OL,11,FConservative neglect.
OL,13,F"Patients and staff alike can see that
OL,14,Fthe NHS is broken. Only Rishi Sunak
OL,15,Fand his party won't acknowledge that
OL,16,Fthe crisis in the NHS is a national
OL,17,Femergency, and if they can't diagnose
OL,18,Fthe illness, then how can they be
OL,19,Ftrusted to cure it?
OL,26,@pD@ROUuD@AOU
