OL,7,F"The NHS is crying out for change and
OL,8,Fonly Labour has a plan to deliver it."
OL,10,FPaul Rees, chief executive of the
OL,11,FNational Pharmacy Association, said:
OL,12,F"Funding pressures have been impacting
OL,13,Fon all parts of the health service,
OL,14,Fincluding vital local community
OL,15,Fpharmacies.
OL,17,F"Community pharmacies have seen a 40%
OL,18,Freduction in their real-terms funding
OL,19,Fsince 2016.
