OL,5,Cwarn
OL,7,F"This has resulted in a sharp rise in
OL,8,Fpharmacy closures, with 10 pharmacies
OL,9,Fclosing a week this year alone and
OL,10,Fmany other pharmacies reducing the
OL,11,Fservices they are able to offer their
OL,12,Fpatients.
OL,14,F"It's imperative that any incoming
OL,15,Fgovernment addresses the crisis in
OL,16,Fprimary care and the looming cliff-
OL,17,Fedge facing pharmacies, which for
OL,18,Fmillions of people are the front door
OL,19,Fto the NHS and a crucial source of
OL,20,Ffrontline health care."
